caption:
Go to @rangoonbistro. Order everything. The crunchy green tea leaves salad, the Mandalay bean fritters, the noodles – we could talk for hours about the noodles 🍜

It’s Burmese food, from some of the best chefs in Portland, who also worked at some of the best restaurants in SE Asia. So it’s no surprise they’ve grown from backyard popup to one of the top restaurants in the city.
